project currently exists as **design/documentation/specification files only** -- there are no actual `.go` source files, `go.mod`, or `Makefile` in this workspace yet. All code must be created from the specifications.\n\n---\n\n### 2. Top-Level Directory Structure\n\n```\n<workspace>/\n├── .sdd_prompt.md              # SDD prompt for the AI (design context)\n├── project.md                  # Project overview and conventions\n├── test_spec.md                # TDD test case specification\n├── changes/\n│   └── AR-001/                 # Current change request: CRD AgentRuntime type definition\n│       ├── proposal.md\n│       ├── design.md\n│       └── tasks.md\n├── sandbox-orchestration/      # Core orchestration (CRDs, WorkloadManager)\n│   ├── design.md               # Most detailed Go package design\n│   └── spec.md                 # Requirements specification\n├── deployment/\n│   ├── client-go.md            # Generated client-go library spec\n│   ├── design.md\n│   └── spec.md\n├── session-routing/            # Router component\n├── session-store/              # Redis/Valkey store\n├── code-execution/             # PicoD execution engine\n├── cli-toolkit/                # Python CLI\n├── python-sdk/                 # Python SDK\n├── idle-cleanup/               # Agentd GC controller\n├── integrations/\n├── ci-cd/\n└── testing/\n    └── agentcube_tdd_manifest.md\n```\n\n---\n\n### 3. Go Module Name and Import Paths\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| **Go module** | `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube` |\n| **Go version** | `1.24.4` (toolchain `go1.24.9`) |\n| **API Group** | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` |\n| **API Version** | `v1alpha1` |\n\nKey import paths referenced in the design:\n- `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` -- CRD types\n- `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/common/types` -- Shared types (SandboxInfo, etc.)\n- `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/api` -- Error helpers, constants\n- `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/workloadmanager` -- HTTP server, reconciler, GC\n- `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/store` -- Session store interface\n- `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/router` -- HTTP router/proxy\n- `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/agentd` -- Idle cleanup controller\n- `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/picod` -- Code execution engine\n- `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go` -- Generated Kubernetes client\n\n---\n\n### 4. pkg/apis Directory Structure (Planned)\n\nPer the design documents, the directory should be:\n\n```\npkg/apis/\n└── runtime/\n    └── v1alpha1/\n        ├── doc.go                    # Package doc + k8s codegen markers\n        ├── groupversion_info.go      # GroupVersion + SchemeBuilder\n        ├── register.go               # Kind metadata + Resource helper\n        ├── agent_type.go             # AgentRuntime CRD types (Core)\n        ├── codeinterpreter_types.go  # CodeInterpreter CRD + shared types\n        └── zz_generated.deepcopy.go  # Auto-generated by controller-gen\n```\n\n---\n\n### 5. Existing CRD Type Patterns (from design.md and sandbox-orchestration/design.md)\n\n#### 5.1 doc.go -- Package Declaration + Codegen Markers\n\n```go\n// +k8s:deepcopy-gen=package\n// +groupName=runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\npackage v1alpha1\n```\n\n#### 5.2 groupversion_info.go -- GroupVersion and Scheme\n\n```go\npackage v1alpha1\n\nimport (\n    \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime/schema\"\n    \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/scheme\"\n)\n\nvar (\n    GroupVersion = schema.GroupVersion{Group: \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\", Version: \"v1alpha1\"}\n    SchemeBuilder = &scheme.Builder{GroupVersion: GroupVersion}\n    AddToScheme = SchemeBuilder.AddToScheme\n)\n```\n\n#### 5.3 register.go -- Kind Metadata\n\n```go\nvar (\n    CodeInterpreterKind             = \"CodeInterpreter\"\n    CodeInterpreterGroupKind        = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"CodeInterpreter\")\n    CodeInterpreterListKind         = \"CodeInterpreterList\"\n    CodeInterpreterGroupVersionKind = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"CodeInterpreter\")\n)\n\nvar (\n    AgentRuntimeKind             = \"AgentRuntime\"\n    AgentRuntimeListKind         = \"AgentRuntimeList\"\n    AgentRuntimeGroupVersionKind = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"AgentRuntime\")\n)\n\nvar SchemeGroupVersion = GroupVersion\n\nfunc Resource(resource string) schema.GroupVersionResource {\n    return GroupVersion.WithResource(resource)\n}\n```\n\n#### 5.4 agent_type.go -- AgentRuntime CRD Types\n\n```go\n// +genclient\n// +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n// +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n// +kubebuilder:subresource:status\n// +kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced\n// +kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"\ntype AgentRuntime struct {\n    metav1.TypeMeta   `json:\",inline\"`\n    metav1.ObjectMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n    Spec   AgentRuntimeSpec   `json:\"spec\"`\n    Status AgentRuntimeStatus `json:\"status,omitempty\"`\n}\n\ntype AgentRuntimeSpec struct {\n    Ports []TargetPort `json:\"targetPort\"`\n    // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n    Template *SandboxTemplate `json:\"podTemplate\" protobuf:\"bytes,1,opt,name=podTemplate\"`\n    // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n    // +kubebuilder:default=\"15m\"\n    SessionTimeout *metav1.Duration `json:\"sessionTimeout,omitempty\" protobuf:\"bytes,2,opt,name=sessionTimeout\"`\n    // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n    // +kubebuilder:default=\"8h\"\n    MaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration `json:\"maxSessionDuration,omitempty\" protobuf:\"bytes,3,opt,name=maxSessionDuration\"`\n}\n\ntype AgentRuntimeStatus struct {\n    // +optional\n    Conditions []metav1.Condition `json:\"conditions,omitempty\"`\n}\n\ntype SandboxTemplate struct {\n    // +optional\n    Labels map[string]string `json:\"labels,omitempty\" protobuf:\"bytes,1,rep,name=labels\"`\n    // +optional\n    Annotations map[string]string `json:\"annotations,omitempty\" protobuf:\"bytes,2,rep,name=annotations\"`\n    // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n    Spec corev1.PodSpec `json:\"spec\" protobuf:\"bytes,3,opt,name=spec\"`\n}\n\n// +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n// +kubebuilder:object:root=true\ntype AgentRuntimeList struct {\n    metav1.TypeMeta `json:\",inline\"`\n    metav1.ListMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n    Items           []AgentRuntime `json:\"items\"`\n}\n```\n\n#### 5.5 codeinterpreter_types.go -- CodeInterpreter + Shared Types\n\n```go\n// +genclient\n// +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n// +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n// +kubebuilder:subresource:status\n// +kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced\n// +kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"\ntype CodeInterpreter struct {\n    metav1.TypeMeta   `json:\",inline\"`\n    metav1.ObjectMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n    Spec   CodeInterpreterSpec   `json:\"spec\"`\n    Status CodeInterpreterStatus `json:\"status,omitempty\"`\n}\n\ntype CodeInterpreterSpec struct {\n    // +optional\n    Ports []TargetPort `json:\"ports,omitempty\"`\n    // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n    Template *CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate `json:\"template\"`\n    // +kubebuilder:default=\"15m\"\n    SessionTimeout *metav1.Duration `json:\"sessionTimeout,omitempty\"`\n    // +kubebuilder:default=\"8h\"\n    MaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration `json:\"maxSessionDuration,omitempty\"`\n    // +optional\n    WarmPoolSize *int32 `json:\"warmPoolSize,omitempty\"`\n    // +kubebuilder:default=\"picod\"\n    // +kubebuilder:validation:Enum=picod;none\n    // +optional\n    AuthMode AuthModeType `json:\"authMode,omitempty\"`\n}\n\ntype CodeInterpreterStatus struct {\n    // +optional\n    Conditions []metav1.Condition `json:\"conditions,omitempty\"`\n    // +optional\n    Ready bool `json:\"ready,omitempty\"`\n}\n\ntype TargetPort struct {\n    // +optional\n    PathPrefix string `json:\"pathPrefix,omitempty\"`\n    // +optional\n    Name string `json:\"name,omitempty\"`\n    Port uint32 `json:\"port\"`\n    // +kubebuilder:default=HTTP\n    // +kubebuilder:validation:Enum=HTTP;HTTPS;\n    Protocol ProtocolType `json:\"protocol\"`\n}\n\ntype ProtocolType string\n\nconst (\n    ProtocolTypeHTTP  ProtocolType = \"HTTP\"\n    ProtocolTypeHTTPS ProtocolType = \"HTTPS\"\n)\n\ntype AuthModeType string\n\nconst (\n    AuthModePicoD AuthModeType = \"picod\"\n    AuthModeNone  AuthModeType = \"none\"\n)\n\n// +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n// +kubebuilder:object:root=true\ntype CodeInterpreterList struct {\n    metav1.TypeMeta `json:\",inline\"`\n    metav1.ListMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n    Items           []CodeInterpreter `json:\"items\"`\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 6. AgentRuntime-Related Files\n\nAll AgentRuntime-related content exists as **design documentation** (not source code):\n\n| File | Content |\n|------|---------|\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-001/design.md` | Full design spec for AgentRuntime CRD types (636 lines) |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-001/proposal.md` | Change proposal for AgentRuntime type definition |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-001/tasks.md` | Task checklist (5 items, all unchecked) |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/sandbox-orchestration/design.md` | Contains Go code snippets for all packages including `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/sandbox-orchestration/spec.md` | Requirements spec with Gherkin-style scenarios |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/.sdd_prompt.md` | SDD prompt with client-go generated interface specs |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/deployment/client-go.md` | Generated client-go library specification |\n\n---\n\n### 7. Task Checklist (tasks.md)\n\nLocated at: `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-001/tasks.md`\n\n```markdown\n# AR-001 任务清单\n\n- [ ] 创建 pkg/apis 目录结构\n- [ ] 定义 AgentRuntime Spec 类型\n- [ ] 定义 AgentRuntime Status 类型\n- [ ] 生成 DeepCopy 方法\n- [ ] 注册到 scheme\n```\n\nAll 5 tasks are currently **unchecked** (not yet implemented).\n\n---\n\n### 8. Key Conventions and Patterns\n\n| Convention | Detail |\n|------------|--------|\n| **Go packages** | Under `pkg/`, binaries under `cmd/` |\n| **JSON tags** | camelCase (e.g., `targetPort`, `podTemplate`) |\n| **Go structs** | PascalCase (e.g., `AgentRuntimeSpec`, `SandboxTemplate`) |\n| **Kubebuilder markers** | `+genclient`, `+kubebuilder:object:root=true`, `+kubebuilder:subresource:status`, `+kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced`, `+kubebuilder:validation:Required`, `+kubebuilder:default=...`, `+kubebuilder:validation:Enum=...` |\n| **DeepCopy generation** | `+k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object` on root types |\n| **Scheme registration** | Via `SchemeBuilder.Register(&Type{}, &TypeList{})` in `init()` |\n| **CRD root type markers** | `+genclient`, `+k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=...`, `+kubebuilder:object:root=true`, `+kubebuilder:subresource:status`, `+kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced`, `+kubebuilder:printcolumn:...` |\n| **List type markers** | `+k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=...`, `+kubebuilder:object:root=true` |\n| **Code generation tools** | `controller-gen` v0.17.2 (DeepCopy + CRD YAML), `k8s.io/code-generator` v0.34.1 (client-go) |\n| **Make targets** | `make generate`, `make gen-crd`, `make gen-client`, `make gen-all` |\n\n---\n\n### 9. Key Dependencies (from go.mod specification)\n\n| Dependency | Version |\n|------------|---------|\n| `k8s.io/api` | v0.34.1 |\n| `k8s.io/apimachinery` | v0.34.1 |\n| `k8s.io/client-go` | v0.34.1 |\n| `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime` | v0.22.2 |\n| `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox` | v0.1.1 |\n| `github.com/gin-gonic/gin` | v1.10.0 |\n| `github.com/redis/go-redis/v9` | v9.17.1 |\n| `github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5` | v5.2.2 |\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_2899e39adffeJr2Qksm2nGUiK8","model":{"modelID":"qwen3.6-plus","providerID":"alibaba-cn"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore agentcube project structure","time":{"start":1775807612495,"end":1775807747120}}}}
